{"tid":1187933,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"野村分析師一張圖驚天預警︰看到雷曼爆煲前的徴兆　美股恐冧40%","createTime":"2019-06-06T03:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T04:52:12.000Z","uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b036ab335ce1d530af5cd47c818137c594fb2fd","tid":1187933,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2880769/org/851cf46b1938ac57671d2d6129bf24a9.PNG/J5TcfdYg2ZzUK9pFZhl6-9cG3azskezr-VFNmflRTZk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2880769%2Forg%2F851cf46b1938ac57671d2d6129bf24a9.PNG%2FJ5TcfdYg2ZzUK9pFZhl6-9cG3azskezr-VFNmflRTZk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=84d04474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》報道，Takada引述一個反映市場恐慌和貪婪的「美國股市情緒指數」，直言美國股市現時的情緒趨勢漸漸與2008年雷曼危機爆發前的模式相似﹙見圖﹚。<br />\n<br />\n根據上述指標走勢，標指可能平均要挫約20%，而最壞情況則暴瀉約40%，與2008年9月雷曼兄弟申請破產後的6個月內，該指數的跌勢睇齊。<br />\n恐處「終極一跌」之前<br />\n<br />\nTakada表示，目前市場模式教人想起2008年6月的情景，投資者當時也在擔心全球經濟增長及股市調整。他指出，大冧市前，2008年7月至8月美股亦曾出現一次安慰性反彈，他表示，股市目前正朝向2008年6月至7月時的情景走。<br />\n<br />\n因此，Takada警告，我們很可能正處於第二次大浪之後，但在「終極一跌」之前，他同時將2018年12月的拋售與2008年1月至3月的拋售潮相提並論。12月傳統上是美股表現良好的月份，但去年12月，市場憂慮聯儲局加息過度觸發衰退，加上華府陷停擺危機，美股道指一周暴瀉1,655點或6.87%，為2008年10月來最差！Takada續稱，這亦是為什麼需要一些驚喜，才能讓市場情緒盡快偏離這種不祥模式的因由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/337353/%E9%87%8E%E6%9D%91%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%9C%96%E9%A9%9A%E5%A4%A9%E9%A0%90%E8%AD%A6-%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E9%9B%B7%E6%9B%BC%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%B4%E5%85%86-%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%81%90%E5%86%A740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F337353%2F%25E9%2587%258E%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259E%2590%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%25A9%259A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%259C%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%259B%25B7%25E6%259B%25BC%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2585%25B2%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25BE%25B4%25E5%2585%2586-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%2586%25A740&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=05b42f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/337353/%E9%87%8E%E6%9D%91%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%9C%96%E9%A9%9A%E5%A4%A9%E9%A0%90%E8%AD%A6-%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E9%9B%B7%E6%9B%BC%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%B4%E5%85%86-%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%81%90%E5%86%A740</a>"},{"pid":"8694c7fdd8c1fb059ed61b47588ae1b7167bde94","tid":1187933,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"有50%股災"},{"pid":"feb3903f5efb0fe3e13ca12aaf86a9c6006e8d17","tid":1187933,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"連登首席分析師唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5dfbd8f4c08bbf234c76a9c006d313e2235b2d","tid":1187933,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:25:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b870c51b4c1f05f55b78389707f8f7fc846b815f","tid":1187933,"uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"數浪去維港啦"},{"pid":"64512eb71c5e3b47b655933ff6b19ad642a5a04c","tid":1187933,"uid":55955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:40:19.000Z","msg":"倒果為因"},{"pid":"cfda7b1e48e520d759836d6231fe78e96b6adb07","tid":1187933,"uid":18886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:49:41.000Z","msg":"講左就唔係啦"},{"pid":"218f81eea892397c286de057a34b32e6c5a46f6e","tid":1187933,"uid":120766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}